server: ssh from
client: ssh to

on server 
ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C "text"
leave location and password blank


on client
sudo adduser student
sudo passwd -l student

on server
ssh-copy-id student@clientip

or cat the key and manually put it in/home/student/.ssh/authorized_keys on client

on client
sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
PubkeyAuthentication yes

restart ssh on client
